      public List<org.trello4j.model.Card> getFinishedSprintBacklog(int sprintNumber) throws IOException
      Gets the ID of cards from the Backlog pertaining to a specific Sprint. This method gets the "Done" list of each sprint and returns a list of the cards on it.
      Parameters:
      sprintNumber - Sprint the user wants the cards from.
      Returns:
      A list of cards from the desired Sprint.
      Throws:

    • getSprintHoursByMember

      public Double[] getSprintHoursByMember(String memberName, int sprintNumber) throws IOException
      Returns a Double array with the number of hours worked, hours estimated and the cost of the hours worked of a given member. This method works by iterating through the "Increment" list of the SPRINT requested and deleting the cards that don't have the member requested on them.
      Parameters:
      sprintNumber - number of the SPRINT.
      memberName - name of the member.
      Returns:
      Double[] with the following format: [HOURS WORKED, HOURS ESTIMATED, COST OF HOURS WORKED].
      Throws:
      IOException - see getBoardListIdByName(String);

    • getCommittedActivitiesByMember

      public Double[] getCommittedActivitiesByMember(String memberName, int sprintNumber) throws IOException
      Returns an array with the amount of committed activities and the total hours worked on those activities by member, as well as the cost. This method works by iterating every "Increment" list of the given SPRINT and removing the cards without the requested member on them.
      Parameters:
      memberName - name of the member.
      sprintNumber - number of the sprint.
      Returns:
      Double[] with the following format [NUMBER OF ACTIVITIES, TOTAL HOURS WORKED, COST OF HOURS WORKED].
      Throws:
      IOException - see getBoardListIdByName(String);
